00:29:52,340 --> 00:29:55,740
Nhưng bố sẽ dành phần đời còn lại của mình

613
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:57,210
để bù đắp cho con.

614
00:29:59,210 --> 00:30:01,050
vì những chuyện khủng khiếp
bố đã làm.

